  "Deploying machine-readable policies on your site": "तपाईंको साइटमा मेसिन-पठनीय नीतिहरू परिनियोजन गर्दै",
  "Disclaimer": "अस्वीकरण",
  "Distinct from human UI, SEO, or plain APIs, the AI Ingestion & Capability Layer gives websites a machine-facing architecture: a Manifest Layer (entry points like /llms.txt and /ai/manifest.json), a Corpus Layer (machine-readable knowledge), a Capability Layer (agent-callable tools), and a Governance Layer (provenance, licensing, versioning). Static-first, upgradeable toward APIs and MCP. Note: in this paper AICL names the ingestion architecture; on this site's protocol pages AICL refers to the AI Content Licensing Layer.": "मानव UI, SEO, वा साधारण API हरूभन्दा फरक, AI Ingestion & Capability Layer ले वेबसाइटहरूलाई मेसिन-लक्षित आर्किटेक्चर दिन्छ: एक Manifest Layer (/llms.txt र /ai/manifest.json जस्ता प्रवेश-विन्दुहरू), एक Corpus Layer (मेसिन-पठनीय ज्ञान), एक Capability Layer (एजेन्ट-आह्वानयोग्य उपकरणहरू), र एक Governance Layer (provenance, इजाजतपत्र, संस्करणीकरण)। स्ट्याटिक-प्राथमिकता, API र MCP तर्फ स्तरोन्नतिजोग्य। नोट: यस पत्रमा AICL ले ingestion आर्किटेक्चरलाई जनाउँछ; यस साइटका प्रोटोकल पृष्ठहरूमा भने AICL ले AI Content Licensing Layer लाई जनाउँछ।",
  "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm": "Do Large Language Models Possess a Theory of Mind? A Comparative Evaluation Using the Strange Stories Paradigm",
  "Docs": "कागजातहरू",
